{"tid":1006341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【轉載】環球經濟寒冬? IDC: 2018年全球手機出貨量下滑 4.1%","createTime":"2019-02-03T02:28:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T03:31:29.000Z","uid":66087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"581d83f70998278a89c0e2d06fe604648199968e","tid":1006341,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T02:28:41.000Z","msg":"2019-01-31 13:15<br />\n<br />\n首頁 &gt; 國際財經<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕2018年為智慧手機出貨表現史上最慘的1年，調研機構 IDC 週三公佈報告指出，2018年第4季智慧手機出貨量3.754億部，年衰退4.9%，已連第5季下降。<br />\n<br />\n去年全球手機出貨量為14億部，年減4.1%，創2018年成為智慧手機出貨表現史上最慘的1年。<strong>其中，中國市場出貨量下滑了10%</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，IDC認為，手機市場表現疲弱，主要是由於更換週期延長、政治和經濟的不確定性增加所致。"},{"pid":"e61ca589c90068ec8f7c10efc441ee59e67d8ad5","tid":1006341,"uid":66087,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T02:29:21.000Z","msg":"去年第4季全球銷量居冠依舊是三星，去年第4季總出貨量7040萬部，年減5.5%，市佔率也從20%下滑到18.7%。<br />\n<br />\n至於第2名則是蘋果，去年第4季出貨量年減11.5%，6840萬部。<br />\n<br />\n第3至5名依序為，華為去年第4季出貨量為6050萬部，年增43.9%；OPPO出貨量為2920萬部，年增6.8%；小米出貨量則為2860萬部，年增1.4%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▼IDC 2018年第4季全球五大智能手機品牌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NbXcyL4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNbXcyL4.png&h=0c92aeaf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"232ebb54474f7f2297b0851a8957ff97355c5cf5","tid":1006341,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T02:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d1c3a353a724e562419a0401bb18e53062ab3b","tid":1006341,"uid":31186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T02:30:36.000Z","msg":"中國啲數據係都要同人地倒轉啲色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5a3d4b1ce8ee0362892ba468992bb407824d85f","tid":1006341,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93d1c3a353a724e562419a0401bb18e53062ab3b","tid":1006341,"uid":31186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T02:30:36.000Z","msg":"中國啲數據係都要同人地倒轉啲色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T02:32:35.000Z","msg":"台灣都係紅升綠降<br />\n香港跟番大英祖國習慣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ae9d016c96d88207ebad098882385f3e80a1b2","tid":1006341,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:00:47.000Z","msg":"經典無價！hTC絕版神機10年回顧曝光「大勝iPhone」<br />\n<a href=\"https://fnc.ebc.net.tw/FncNews/life/69206\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffnc.ebc.net.tw%2FFncNews%2Flife%2F69206&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7tagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=3b4521d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fnc.ebc.net.tw/FncNews/life/69206</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-fnc.ebc.net.tw/EbcFnc/news/2019/02/01/1549034794_20751.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-fnc.ebc.net.tw%2FEbcFnc%2Fnews%2F2019%2F02%2F01%2F1549034794_20751.jpg&h=c2900b6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日htc在微博跟風10年挑戰，秀出過往推出過的智慧型手機。( 圖 / 維基百科 )<br />\n<br />\n你的第一支智慧型手機是htc嗎？近期網路上吹起了一波懷舊風潮，像是10年挑戰計劃等，宏達電也趕上這波潮流，在官方微博公布，只要轉發貼文就有機會拿到「htc經典老機型」，此文一推出後，引發網友們熱烈討論，大推當年的One系列、M8超經典。"},{"pid":"02f094117577a2acb4400bd894679515fa665221","tid":1006341,"uid":89861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:31:29.000Z","msg":"同經濟冇關、手機發展去到樽頸，上年部機同今年新機唔差得遠，用部機上下網點解要比錢換～"}]}